726300f-d.title: Queens: Calamus Avenue - 71st Street
726300f-d.text:
Calamus Ave., south side, east from 71st Street, showing at
the right the M. Pinkney house which was in the family from 1860
to 1891. One Howard owned it in 1910. This is a set of four views.
April 1925.
Views 1 and 2.
View 3: March 1923.
View 4: March 1923 .
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
